node.text: So proud of my friend and trusted acting partner, @winstoncduke and his colleagues behind the exceptional, thought-provoking film #NineDays. How writer/director @edson.oda creates a world both earnest and unsentimental is beyond me. This is the kind of narrative experience that invites you to slow down, absorb, contemplate and reevaluate what it means to possess the gift of life. A value add for sure. #runandgoseeit @sonyclassics @zaziebeetz @wongrel
